\begin{document}$$ F_1 =\frac{\left| {\chi _1^2 -\chi _2^2 } \right|}{\chi _1^2 }\left({n-1} \right),$$\end{document}where n, the sample size = 200 and n−1 is the number of degrees of freedom.
